description	"RAB-24

^2Weaponry:
- Disruptor Rifle (2)
-- Overload Modifications [Shots Pass Through Walls]

^6Inventory:
- Portable Sentry Gun

^3Abilities:
- Tracking Darts (3) ^3[CS2]

RAB-24 used to be a protocol droid until his master Buz'eet Thudos had him reprogrammed.
Now he is one of Thudos' many instruments of destruction, with no knowledge of the concept of mercy.

A favoured weapon of RAB-24 is the Disruptor, an illegal firearm capable of disintegrating a humanoid target to a mere pile of ash.
With certain modifications, Disruptors can be effective against hardened targets, such as starship hulls, or armoured vehicles.
When completely charged, such modified weapons are capable of burning through walls and vaporizing targets on the other side."